data.description: Back on the market.The loan is assumable at 4.7%!! This home is located in the prestigious North Ranch area of Westlake Village. This elegantly remodeled residence boasts high-quality features and fine craftsmanship. Some key highlights of this stunning property.     Location: Situated in the highly sought-after North Ranch area, this home enjoys the prestige of being adjacent to the North Ranch Country Club and surrounded by multi-million dollar homes, showcasing the exclusivity of the neighborhood.    Interior: The grand entrance with travertine floors sets the tone for the opulence within. The formal dining room seamlessly connects to the spacious living room, featuring high ceilings and elegant shutters throughout. The inclusion of a wet bar adds an element of sophistication to the living space.    Kitchen: The kitchen has undergone a complete transformation with top-tier cabinets and granite countertops. Modern amenities such as double ovens and a convenient pull-out pantry are included, catering to both functionality and style.    Family Room: The warm and inviting family room boasts custom bookcases, adding a touch of personalization to the space. This room effortlessly flows into the lush backyard, which features a private pool and spa. The covered patio is the perfect setting for outdoor dining and relaxation.    Primary Bedroom: The primary bedroom exudes luxury with its high ceilings and cozy fireplace. A cedar-lined closet adds a touch of elegance and practicality. The ensuite primary bathroom is beautifully appointed with dual sinks, a redesigned shower, and a tub for relaxation.    Additional Bedrooms: Two more spacious bedrooms offer ample accommodation for residents or guests. Another updated bathroom ensures modern comfort and style.    Community Amenities: The community's offerings include a pool, spa, and recreational room, providing additional opportunities for relaxation and entertainment.    Nearby Attractions: The property's proximity to a park, restaurants, the lake, golf courses, and excellent schools enriches the lifestyle and convenience for its residents.    In summary, this elegant home in the prestigious North Ranch area of Westlake Village offers a luxurious and refined living experience. Its meticulous remodeling, high-quality finishes, and desirable location make it a standout property within an upscale community.
